{"tid":667233,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食鬼亂煮系列---Buttermilk granola","createTime":"2018-05-16T14:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T13:27:45.000Z","uid":182683,"like":42,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ed54493a9224632c5e83e53a5b26aa0b05721b","tid":667233,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"上次整完乳酪,就咁食係差咁d野,加埋granola就perfect池!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出邊買o既granola多數都好甜,最慘就係成日有我最唔鍾意食o既提子乾,有提子乾既野食應該拎去餵狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n我敢講依個recipe一定會係你食過最好食,唔甜,最香口,最脆o既granola!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最正就係你自己想落咩就落咩,又健康又正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/l65Yjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2Fl65Yjf.jpg&h=1d5b8955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次用既材料會比較多,但係做法極簡單,撈幾撈拎去焗就搞掂,整一次夠你食一個月,想整多D自己計番份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且有d材料係個人喜好,可落可唔落,落幾多由你決定,你想點整都得!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n材料:<br />\n麥片 340g(用old fashion rolled oats)<br />\nWheat bran 40g(大間惠康有)<br />\nFlaxseeds 40g(大間惠康有)<br />\n<br />\nButtermilk 225g(建議citysuper買buttermilk粉可以自己用先溝,普通一盒盒都有,但好快過期同比較貴)<br />\n牛油 115g (叮溶佢)<br />\n白糖 200g<br />\n少少鹽<br />\n---------------------------------<br />\n配料:<br />\n<br />\n開心果, 切碎 90g<br />\n杏仁, 切碎 85g<br />\n合桃, 切碎 80g<br />\n紅莓乾(Cranberry) 200g<br />\n(配料你可以根據個人喜好買唔同配料,分量你整多幾次可以自己調配,但要注意個比例,因為落得太多莓乾類既野會好甜)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做法:<br />\n<br />\n1. 焗爐較170&deg;C.<br />\n磅曬所有野先,麥片,wheat bran,flaxseeds放埋一齊;牛油,buttermilk分開磅;果仁磅埋一齊,紅莓分開放.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/XNPjdB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2FXNPjdB.jpg&h=ef644d99&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/ehr15d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2Fehr15d.jpg&h=9d09cb9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 麥片,wheat bran,flaxseeds撈混,倒buttermilk同牛油落去,撈混沌搵塊布冚住等20分鐘.<br />\n之後落糖,撈到見唔到有好大點糖就可以,又係搵塊布冚住等30分鐘.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/LgQmbh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2FLgQmbh.jpg&h=26bca311&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/Kqh6VI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2FKqh6VI.jpg&h=ec381665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/TQCSIy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2FTQCSIy.jpg&h=03b9a708&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/p2f8Kg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2Fp2f8Kg.jpg&h=b6b9ef1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 等緊既時間就可以處理果仁,切碎果仁,大細隨你鍾意.<br />\n之後用焗盤鋪平焗7-10分鐘,焗到有少少啡色就可以,放埋一邊備用.<br />\n個焗爐校番150&deg;C.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/neUafP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2FneUafP.jpg&h=b88449f8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/bk3qr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2Fbk3qr6.jpg&h=b36844cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 過左30分鐘,你望望個麥片個堆野盆底有少少液體,咁姐係D糖溶曬,可以去下一步,如果冇就等多陣.<br />\n焗盤鋪牛油紙,將麥片鋪係焗盤,盡量鋪平D,然後入爐.<br />\n每隔25分鐘拎出黎用兩支叉刮底將底個D刮番上黎,將邊個D堆番去中間(邊位痴住個盤受熱會快上色過中間),依個步驟要快手,唔好比盤野降溫太多.<br />\n你會見到一次比一次深色,焗到75分鐘撈完最後一次之後,要小心睇色(人人個焗爐溫度都有分別),焗到金黃色就可以出爐.<br />\n我個人鍾意焗深色少少,會脆D同有焦香味.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/Xm6u0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2FXm6u0s.jpg&h=88d68116&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/0196j7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F0196j7.jpg&h=4989d032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/38fmLO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F38fmLO.jpg&h=4d06a33c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.最後出爐仲熱果時倒落果仁同紅莓乾個盆野搞混,倒番落個焗盤等到唔熱就可以入盒,搞掂!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/YsR3bQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2FYsR3bQ.jpg&h=2437f8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/16/5IXWc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F5IXWc8.jpg&h=ac1c166a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早餐咁樣食po張相上ig d囡畏以為你係鬼佬都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:hkfoodghost<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68463567930c231bad1f271a5c1507344cc8e86b","tid":667233,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ca99bba1b3451028dc84e036f0dc0deaffda9b","tid":667233,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68463567930c231bad1f271a5c1507344cc8e86b","tid":667233,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c10b7fb84739046